Ray Milland starred and directed this low-budget film.<br>
<br>
An ordinary suburban family is out camping when nuclear armagedon strikes. All they see is the sky lighting up in the distance.<br>
<br>
From then on it is how to survive. The father is willing to do anything to ensure the family's survival. The mother cannot accept anything that violates their sense of Right and Wrong.<br>
<br>
